{
  "id": "69afc830213039996822f62c",
  "title": "ゆるトーク:枯れた技術",
  "created": 1773127786,
  "updated": 1773138675,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69afc830213039996822f62c",
      "text": "ゆるトーク:枯れた技術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127786,
      "updated": 1773127786
    },
    {
      "id": "69aff2ed000000000073c22b",
      "text": "[枯れた技術]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773138670,
      "updated": 1773138675
    },
    {
      "id": "69aff2ef000000000073c22c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773138672,
      "updated": 1773138672
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86a00000000003b9e1e",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（進行）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127786,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e1f",
      "text": "ねえねえ、今日のテーマなんだけどさー。「枯れた技術」ってやつ！🌱",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e20",
      "text": "なんか字面だけ見ると「古くて終わった技術」って感じするよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e21",
      "text": "でもオタク界隈とかエンジニア界隈だと、むしろ良い意味で使うらしいんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e22",
      "text": "りか先生、そのへんkwsk（くわしく）！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e23",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e24",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e25",
      "text": "了解。結論から言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e26",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e27",
      "text": "枯れた技術（Mature Technology）とは、長い時間使われて問題が出尽くし、信頼性が高い技術のこと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e28",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e29",
      "text": "新しい技術は革新的だが、未知のバグや運用リスクが多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e2a",
      "text": "対して枯れた技術は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e2b",
      "text": " 挙動が安定",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e2c",
      "text": " ノウハウが蓄積されている",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e2d",
      "text": " トラブルシュートが容易",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e2e",
      "text": "つまり、安全性を優先する設計では非常に強い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e2f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e30",
      "text": "有名な例としては、任天堂の思想。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e31",
      "text": "「[枯れた技術の水平思考]」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e32",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e33",
      "text": "参考：",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e34",
      "text": "https://www.nintendo.co.jp/ir/library/events/101029/04.html",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e35",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e36",
      "text": "新技術ではなく、既存技術を別の形で組み合わせて価値を作るという考え方だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e37",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e38",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e39",
      "text": "あー！！それ聞いたことある！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e3a",
      "text": "ゲームボーイとかだよね？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e3b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e3c",
      "text": "なんか当時のスペックって、わりとショボ…いや控えめ？だったんでしょ？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e3d",
      "text": "でもめっちゃ売れたやつ！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e3e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e3f",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e40",
      "text": "その通り。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e41",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e42",
      "text": "例えば1989年のゲームボーイ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e43",
      "text": "当時すでにカラー液晶技術は存在していた。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e44",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e45",
      "text": "だが任天堂はあえて",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e46",
      "text": " モノクロ液晶",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e47",
      "text": " 低消費電力CPU",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e48",
      "text": "という枯れた技術を採用した。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e49",
      "text": "結果として",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e4a",
      "text": " 電池が長持ち（約30時間）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e4b",
      "text": " 価格が安い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e4c",
      "text": " 故障が少ない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e4d",
      "text": "という強みを得た。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e4e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e4f",
      "text": "これは技術選択として合理的。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e50",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e51",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e52",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e53",
      "text": "なんだか、技術にも「年の功」があるのですね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e55",
      "text": "人もまた、若い頃は勢いがありますけれど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e56",
      "text": "長い歳月を重ねると、静かな強さを持つようになりますでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e57",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e58",
      "text": "枯れた技術という言葉も、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e59",
      "text": "まるで秋の庭の木々のように――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e5a",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e5b",
      "text": "派手さはなくとも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e5c",
      "text": "長く人の暮らしを支えてくれるもの、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e5d",
      "text": "そういう響きがいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e5e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e5f",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e60",
      "text": "あー、なんか詩人きたｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e61",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e62",
      "text": "でもたしかにさ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e63",
      "text": "最新＝正義ってわけでもないんだよね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e64",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e65",
      "text": "スマホアプリとかでも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e66",
      "text": "「最新フレームワーク使ったら逆にバグ地獄」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e67",
      "text": "みたいな話、ネットでよく見るｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e68",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e69",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e6a",
      "text": "それは現実に多い。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e6b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e6c",
      "text": "ソフトウェアでも同じ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e6d",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e6e",
      "text": "例えばWeb開発では",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e6f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e70",
      "text": "実績のある技術（枯れている）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e71",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e72",
      "text": " HTML",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e73",
      "text": " CSS",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e74",
      "text": " SQL",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e75",
      "text": " Linux",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e76",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e77",
      "text": "これらは数十年の運用実績がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e78",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e79",
      "text": "一方、毎年のように新しいフレームワークが生まれる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e7a",
      "text": "だが",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e7b",
      "text": " ドキュメント不足",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e7c",
      "text": " コミュニティ未成熟",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e7d",
      "text": " 突然の開発終了",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e7e",
      "text": "などのリスクがある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e7f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e80",
      "text": "エンジニアの世界ではよく言う。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e81",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e82",
      "text": "「新しい技術は、十分枯れるまで待て」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e83",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e84",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e85",
      "text": "うわーそれ深い…",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e86",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e87",
      "text": "ゲームでも似てるかも。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e88",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e89",
      "text": "最新エンジンで作った超リアルゲーが",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e8a",
      "text": "バグまみれで炎上して、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e8b",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e8c",
      "text": "逆にドット絵ゲームが神ゲー扱いとか",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e8d",
      "text": "普通にあるしｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e8e",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e8f",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e90",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e91",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e92",
      "text": "それはまるで、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e93",
      "text": "豪華なお料理よりも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e94",
      "text": "長く作り続けられてきた家庭の味が",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e95",
      "text": "人の心をあたためることがある――",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e96",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e97",
      "text": "そんな情景に似ていますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e98",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e99",
      "text": "技術もまた、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e9a",
      "text": "人が長く触れてきたものほど、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e9b",
      "text": "手になじむのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e9c",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e9d",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e9e",
      "text": "補足すると、誤解されがちな点がある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9e9f",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea0",
      "text": "枯れた技術 ≠ 古いだけの技術",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea2",
      "text": "重要なのは",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea3",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea4",
      "text": "「十分に検証されている」こと。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea6",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea7",
      "text": " 信頼性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea8",
      "text": " 再現性",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ea9",
      "text": " 知識の蓄積",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eaa",
      "text": "この三点が揃っている技術。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eab",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eac",
      "text": "だから航空宇宙や医療では、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ead",
      "text": "むしろ新技術は慎重に導入される。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eae",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eaf",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb0",
      "text": "あーそれめっちゃわかる！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb2",
      "text": "飛行機とかで",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb3",
      "text": "「最新OS入れました！」とか言われたら",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb4",
      "text": "むしろ怖いｗｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb6",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb7",
      "text": "（うなずく）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eb9",
      "text": "確かに……空の旅は、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eba",
      "text": "新しさよりも安心が大切でございますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ebb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ebc",
      "text": "人の命を預かる場所では、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ebd",
      "text": "静かに積み重ねられた信頼こそ、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ebe",
      "text": "何より尊いのでしょう。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ebf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec0",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec1",
      "text": "結論をまとめる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec3",
      "text": "枯れた技術の価値",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec4",
      "text": " 信頼性が高い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec5",
      "text": " ノウハウが豊富",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec6",
      "text": " コストが低い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec7",
      "text": " トラブル対応が容易",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec8",
      "text": "つまり",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ec9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eca",
      "text": "「堅実なシステムには最適」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ecb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ecc",
      "text": "ただし欠点もある。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ecd",
      "text": " 性能の限界",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ece",
      "text": " 革新性が低い",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ecf",
      "text": "だから理想は",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed0",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed1",
      "text": "新技術と枯れた技術のバランス。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed3",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]（まとめ）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed4",
      "text": "なるほどねー！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed6",
      "text": "つまり今日の結論はこれ👇",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed7",
      "text": " 最新＝神じゃない！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed8",
      "text": " 枯れた技術＝安心と実績のかたまり！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ed9",
      "text": "ってことだね！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eda",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9edb",
      "text": "いやーオタク的にも納得。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9edc",
      "text": "ゲームでもアニメでも",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9edd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ede",
      "text": "「古典は強い」",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9edf",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee0",
      "text": "ってよく言うしね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee2",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee3",
      "text": "（微笑）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee5",
      "text": "長く愛されるものには、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee6",
      "text": "きっと理由があるのでしょうね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee8",
      "text": "古い本のページをめくるときのように、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ee9",
      "text": "少しだけ色あせた技術にも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eea",
      "text": "人の知恵がそっと宿っている気がいたします。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eeb",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eec",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eed",
      "text": "……悪くない表現だ。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eee",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9eef",
      "text": "技術の世界でも、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef0",
      "text": "時間は最高のテスト環境だから。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef1",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef2",
      "text": "[[ふーこ.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef3",
      "text": "うおー！なんか最後かっこよく締まった！",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef4",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef5",
      "text": "じゃあ次回のテーマどうする？",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef6",
      "text": "「黒歴史プログラミング言語」とか？ｗ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef7",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef8",
      "text": "[[りか.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9ef9",
      "text": "それは少し語りが長くなる。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9efa",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9efb",
      "text": "[[あや.icon]]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9efc",
      "text": "（静かに笑う）",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc86b00000000003b9efd",
      "text": "りかさんのお話、きっと長編になりますね。",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127787,
      "updated": 1773127787
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc87d00000000003b9efe",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127805,
      "updated": 1773127805
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc87d00000000003b9eff",
      "text": "#2026-03-10",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127805,
      "updated": 1773127820
    },
    {
      "id": "69afc87f00000000003b9f00",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1773127807,
      "updated": 1773127807
    }
  ]
}